{"tid":1972331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11.17營救理大 24歲男認管武器等3罪 判囚10個月","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T15:09:02.000Z","uid":134087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d122a41a19e7c66c2dd13419fa65d0f9d1ff419f","tid":1972331,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"去年11月警方包圍理大校園，並稱要以暴動罪拘捕踏出校園的示威者，引起大批市民「營救」。警方在理大附近截捕一名24歲男子，他早前承認三項控罪，分別是一項管有違禁武器(重力操作棒)、一項《簡易程序治罪條例》下的管有攻擊性武器(摺刀、鋸刀)及一項《公安條例》下的公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪(丫叉及208粒鋼珠)。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官今在九龍城裁判法院接納被告存有真誠悔意，判分別以9、12和18個月監禁為三項控罪的量刑起點，鑑於羅認罪和存有悔意，獲扣減三分一刑期，並同期執行。嚴官考慮年輕因素再作扣減後，總刑期為10個月。嚴官又寄語他日後行事勿衝動，須「三思而後行」。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年11月17日理大校園遭警方包圍，其中一隊警察於晚上8時許到達科學館道近麼地道交界，目睹羅與另外20名黑衣人士逃走，截停被告後，在其右邊褲袋搜出一把摺刀，在背囊搜出一支重力操作棒、一袋共208粒鋼珠、一支丫叉及盔甲等。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\nclick 入link 支持黃色媒體</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072444&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=a8618dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072444&h=98ff4b8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072444</a></span>"},{"pid":"6c6d916dd98435b7476b7f5720afa6b7d0cc761c","tid":1972331,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c206a5d96e7171c5a4453079bfe886c6e2bfa093","tid":1972331,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6f0882e884ecdb14407920c189d181a4036297","tid":1972331,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"24碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65e8e7bb4e9e587b79a5d60d93147301cf8da1a","tid":1972331,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5266e3fe62abb50ec2fac0faa4dbcc5800989224","tid":1972331,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"叫輕判<br />\n睇黎POPO同DOJ想係短時間內縮細示威人數"},{"pid":"fe241fc02518c8242ef84333a4cd9c1b5e9809af","tid":1972331,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"手足需三思而後行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac32cc4e0afa5394b5f414addcccde33d8e2e75","tid":1972331,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee49d8aee344469319203741e8f84723649e7833","tid":1972331,"uid":312698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"又係九龍城個個姓嚴個仆街？"}]}